{"tid":142844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有聽過｢上帝的教會｣？","createTime":"2017-03-04T06:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T03:49:10.000Z","uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"644367356e733157e483dc1369d3945bbbce5036","tid":142844,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"最近有朋友番緊尼間教會 - hkwmscog<br />\n亦都叫我一齊番 咁我都應承左去望望咩料<br />\n而我上網睇佢啲資料真係覺得好可疑<br />\n有無巴打對尼個教會有相關認識？"},{"pid":"818b9dad966df04bd77e38694e7d1e6ba21b279f","tid":142844,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:46:11.000Z","msg":"番緊連教"},{"pid":"fc57d506446df20dc8e4ccf99e39b420d487fba6","tid":142844,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"有咩怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee596dfa8ed1719b5ebc05c032453d89e59f4c1","tid":142844,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番緊連教</blockquote><br />\n咁我都睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e5e19c1ca0b552e40c249381f5cdf4acf51983","tid":142844,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網頁講 天上的母親 - 耶路撒冷<br />\n可以我唔係好熟讀聖經 我唔敢講啲咩<br />\n但再睇其他相關的資訊 <br />\n安商洪、上帝證人會<br />\n有啲感到疑惑<br />\n唔知道真實詳情唔敢亂下結論<br />\n所以想知道更多詳情"},{"pid":"4871e4b74104817eec7131d215b501c89310fff5","tid":142844,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"聽個名都覺怪"},{"pid":"271d7b3324e75c10eb914570d7536d0279605d8f","tid":142844,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"可能係異端"},{"pid":"9a3e2651567b9c90edafa8fce1854eb1a9abdaa0","tid":142844,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT